{"tid":2313052,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實毒L 係人類文明一個進化嘅過程","createTime":"2020-12-05T13:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T13:44:01.000Z","uid":385515,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b001f96b04bb85100cc42c5395a3551a13ff541","tid":2313052,"uid":385515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"人類文明將會去到另一階段，就係兩性之間失去倚賴性。<br />\n毒毒就係當中一個痛苦嘅進化過程，意味著將來嘅男人會由群居者進化成可單獨生存的生命體，係進化前則需要受到性慾以及孤獨的長期折磨。<br />\n當進入成熟期後，荷爾蒙退減，就會正式進化成無需異性獨自生存的新人類，佢哋有著自行平衡陰陽同控制性慾的能力。<br />\n佢哋會比正常人更長命更加聰明，肍肉易更加發達。最後跳出繁殖交配的輪迴<br />\n當然進化亦需各方面配合，例如唔好打飛機同自然飲食等等"},{"pid":"c08c538b592d0e8d9c4b2339f309e06f34ff642e","tid":2313052,"uid":316590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T13:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/facebook/000/032/479/Screen_Shot_2020-01-17_at_1.25.27_PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fentries%2Ficons%2Ffacebook%2F000%2F032%2F479%2FScreen_Shot_2020-01-17_at_1.25.27_PM.jpg&h=79825b1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"532257ebf26324c941020efa6034e089ddebfdf9","tid":2313052,"uid":384679,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T13:04:47.000Z","msg":"咁你咁講宅女都係啦"},{"pid":"110e511a9b017af12bab3180b2e074687fd487fb","tid":2313052,"uid":385515,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"532257ebf26324c941020efa6034e089ddebfdf9","tid":2313052,"uid":384679,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T13:04:47.000Z","msg":"咁你咁講宅女都係啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T13:14:24.000Z","msg":"無錯，女性都會一樣，最後分開成不同物種，靠試管繁殖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而個啲仍然需要倚靠性慾過活嘅，將會永遠被精蟲蠶食頭腦，最後再次退化成動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979935195fb4efdb20cfff310b1e25120342ed07","tid":2313052,"uid":172